comments: Adebayo (MIA) sets the pick in DeRozan's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
DeRozan (SAS) makes marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Butler (MIA) reaches in and makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) during his driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on DeRozan (SAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  DeRozan reaches in and makes contact with Butler (MIA) that affects his SQBR, but the contact occurs before he gathers and it is a personal foul and not a shooting foul as called on the floor.
Belinelli (SAS) and Robinson (MIA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Belinelli (SAS) is not in a legal guarding position when he initiates contact with Butler's (MIA) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) sets the pick in White's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Belinelli (SAS) and Robinson (MIA) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Belinelli (SAS) makes incidental contact with Butler (MIA) after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Butler (MIA) makes contact with the ball, but does not dislodge it before making contact with White's (SAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Mills (SAS) legally contests Robinson's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) holds Nunn's (MIA) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Robinson (MIA) commits a take foul on Belinelli (SAS).
Adebayo (MIA) sets the screen in White's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
